&lt;p&gt;LINE OF WORK AND FLEXIBL SHIFTS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working bank is the ultimate in flexibility without compromising your career. We are looking to recruit qualified RGNs with experience in ITU Critical Care or HDU who are looking for flexible or full time hours to work in our friendly community-minded hospital, easily accessible from London and the surrounding area and working as part of a real team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To join, you must:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Currently be registered with the NMC&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Be eligible to work in the UK&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Pass an enhanced DBS check&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Have a minimum of 6 months relevant experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer great rates, access to the NHS pension, free core skills training and the support of a professional and friendly team from the moment you register with us, to your first shift and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
